channel.title: Should I?
channel.description: Hey Moparscape I was looking around on some different community's & saw a lot of 317's being made/hosted/projected I was wondering if I should keep on doing what I am doing as for keep on coding my 614 and host it. Or either should I quit 614 & make a 317 project thread for a Project Insanity base? Please if you have any answers please vote on the poll & comment below thanks. :P
